section.def:
ashes
                (骨灰) mean ashes resulting from the cremation of
            human remains;

paragraph.content:
in the case of an application made in respect of a still-born child, by a
                    certificate issued in accordance with section 18 of the Births and
                    Deaths Registration Ordinance (Cap. 174);

tr.td:
that I am satisfied that
                            the death of the above-named deceased person was not due to poison,
                            violence or any illegal operation or to privation or neglect;
